[src:rbac-access-control/identity-and-access-management] Identity federation comprises one or more systems that share user access and allow users to log in based on authenticating against one of the systems participating in the federation.
[src:rbac-access-control/identity-and-access-management] This trust between several systems is often known as a "circle of trust".
